WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.320 --> 00:00:06.790
She's not here.

2
00:00:09.680 --> 00:00:11.477
<i>Aah!</i>

3
00:00:11.600 --> 00:00:14.990
Get back! Who are you?

4
00:00:16.080 --> 00:00:18.833
Who are you?

5
00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:24.112
- I'm Willow Ufgood.
- What are you doing here?

6
00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:27.676
I've come to find
the great sorceress. Fin Raziel.

7
00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:30.268
That's me!
I'm Raziel!

8
00:00:32.240 --> 00:00:34.037
This can't be right!

9
00:00:34.160 --> 00:00:37.516
One of Bavmorda's spells
transformed me.

10
00:00:39.760 --> 00:00:42.194
Believe me. it could
have been worse!

11
00:00:42.320 --> 00:00:47.792
Oh. Well. this wand is for you.
It's from Cherlindrea.

12
00:00:47.920 --> 00:00:52.232
Then the prophecy is true.
The princess has been born.

13
00:00:52.360 --> 00:00:54.191
Take me to her.

14
00:00:56.680 --> 00:00:59.274
It is Elora Danan.

15
00:00:59.400 --> 00:01:02.153
<i>Isn't she beautiful?</i>

16
00:01:02.280 --> 00:01:05.078
<i>Isn't she beautiful?</i>

17
00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:08.476
- That's Raziel?
- I don't know. I-

18
00:01:08.600 --> 00:01:10.716
I expected something
more grand. Less. uh-

19
00:01:10.840 --> 00:01:12.637
- Fuzzy.
- Fuzzy!

20
00:01:12.760 --> 00:01:16.389
You must use the wand.
Turn me back into my human form.

21
00:01:16.520 --> 00:01:19.671
- What do I do?
- You mean you're not a sorcerer?

22
00:01:20.920 --> 00:01:23.275
Yes. Sorta.

23
00:01:23.400 --> 00:01:25.755
<i>I'm a farmer.</i>

24
00:01:25.880 --> 00:01:27.632
But I do know a few tricks.

25
00:01:27.760 --> 00:01:32.788
Tricks? Cherlindrea sent you?
You must learn real magic.

26
00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:36.879
<i>Horses! Horses!</i>

27
00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:39.355
<i>Quick! Take her!
Hurry! Hurry!</i>

28
00:01:47.840 --> 00:01:50.673
I knew he was a traitor!

29
00:01:53.200 --> 00:01:55.714
- Sorry about this. peck.
- Keep your mouth shut!

30
00:01:56.800 --> 00:01:59.394
Told you we'd find him
without your help.

31
00:01:59.520 --> 00:02:01.351
- Give me that baby.
- No!

32
00:02:04.720 --> 00:02:08.508
- Give her back!
- Leave me alone! Don't touch me!

33
00:02:14.200 --> 00:02:15.952
This is the one
we're looking for.

34
00:02:16.080 --> 00:02:19.311
<i>We must take it back to Nockmaar.</i>

35
00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:23.831
Lose your skirt?

36
00:02:31.240 --> 00:02:33.037
I've still got what counts.

37
00:02:33.160 --> 00:02:35.355
Not for long.

38
00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:44.310
- Bring him.
- Over here!

39
00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:52.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

40
00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:03.920
We'll never keep up
with those horses.

41
00:03:04.040 --> 00:03:07.237
- Then we will have to track them.
- That would take forever.

42
00:03:07.360 --> 00:03:09.954
Besides. even if we find them.
they'll catch us.

43
00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:13.072
stick us in cages. torture us
and finally devour us.

44
00:03:13.200 --> 00:03:15.031
Are you suggesting
we go home?

45
00:03:15.160 --> 00:03:17.913
- Nah. This is more fun!
- All right.

46
00:03:18.040 --> 00:03:19.871
Fine. then.
Come on!

47
00:03:33.160 --> 00:03:36.391
I'm worried about Elora.
She doesn't sound good.

48
00:03:36.520 --> 00:03:39.114
Hurry! Practise
the chant I taught you!

49
00:03:39.240 --> 00:03:44.758
<i>Tanna... looatha- Oh. I can't
remember the middle part.</i>

50
00:03:44.880 --> 00:03:46.757
<i>Locktwaar!</i>

51
00:03:46.880 --> 00:03:49.713
That's the word
that pleads for change.

52
00:03:49.840 --> 00:03:51.637
<i>Locktwaar.</i>

53
00:03:55.240 --> 00:03:58.198
Elora's cold and hungry.
She knows me.

54
00:03:58.320 --> 00:04:00.117
Please. let me take care of her.

55
00:04:00.240 --> 00:04:02.231
I don't need help from a peck.

56
00:04:05.880 --> 00:04:09.714
- What are you staring at?
- Your leg.

57
00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:12.070
I'd like to break it.

58
00:04:12.200 --> 00:04:14.668
You may find that
difficult. slave.

59
00:04:14.800 --> 00:04:16.836
while I'm up here
and you're down there.

60
00:04:19.840 --> 00:04:21.956
I hate that woman.

61
00:04:53.320 --> 00:04:55.231
Hyah!

62
00:04:58.960 --> 00:05:01.599
I found it. Kael.

63
00:05:02.680 --> 00:05:05.558
<i>That should make
my mother happy.</i>

64
00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:08.558
What are they gonna do to her?

65
00:05:20.600 --> 00:05:23.160
<i>Hither walha...</i>

66
00:05:23.280 --> 00:05:26.590
<i>bairn deru bordak...</i>

67
00:05:26.720 --> 00:05:28.517
<i>bellanockt.</i>

68
00:05:28.640 --> 00:05:31.359
That's magic?
Smells terrible.

69
00:05:31.480 --> 00:05:34.517
- It's the life spark. It forms after-
- Well. it stinks!

70
00:05:34.640 --> 00:05:37.632
- This whole thing stinks!
- Ignore him. Willow.

71
00:05:37.760 --> 00:05:40.593
- He's a fool!
- If only I had a sword!

72
00:05:40.720 --> 00:05:43.632
If only you'd quit talking about it.

73
00:05:43.760 --> 00:05:46.957
Willow. you must transform me
to my human self.

74
00:05:47.080 --> 00:05:49.719
But. Raziel. I'm not ready yet.

75
00:05:49.840 --> 00:05:52.912
You'd better be.
Get me down.

76
00:05:56.400 --> 00:05:58.709
Ow!

77
00:06:01.240 --> 00:06:04.118
Why don't you help me get out of here
instead of chattering with that muskrat?

78
00:06:04.240 --> 00:06:06.800
Muskrat!
When I change back...

79
00:06:06.920 --> 00:06:10.674
to my former self.
I will crush this army.

80
00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:13.268
and take Elora Danan
to Tir Asleen...

81
00:06:13.400 --> 00:06:15.834
<i>where she will be safe.</i>

82
00:06:15.960 --> 00:06:18.155
Ow!

83
00:06:18.280 --> 00:06:20.077
What'd you bite me for?

84
00:06:20.200 --> 00:06:23.317
You need three drops
of your blood to put in the potion.

85
00:06:23.440 --> 00:06:26.557
Well. you coulda warned me.

86
00:06:26.680 --> 00:06:28.955
For beginners.
there's some pain.

87
00:06:29.080 --> 00:06:33.949
<i>but don't let anything
break your concentration.</i>

88
00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:41.593
<i>Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.</i>

89
00:06:41.720 --> 00:06:45.269
- Hello. everybody! We have arrived!
- You are saved.

90
00:06:45.400 --> 00:06:48.073
<i>- Shh!
- Don't interrupt.</i>

91
00:06:49.520 --> 00:06:52.478
<i>Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.</i>

92
00:06:52.600 --> 00:06:55.319
What are you going
to look like if this works?

93
00:06:55.440 --> 00:06:57.749
- Don't interrupt.
- Sorry.

94
00:06:57.880 --> 00:06:59.677
<i>Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.</i>

95
00:06:59.800 --> 00:07:02.951
I am a young.
beautiful woman.

96
00:07:03.080 --> 00:07:04.752
Concentrate. Willow.

97
00:07:04.880 --> 00:07:06.871
<i>Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.</i>

98
00:07:07.000 --> 00:07:09.230
Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.

99
00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:11.351
No!
You're losing me!

100
00:07:11.480 --> 00:07:14.711
<i>Hither greenan bairn claideb lunanockt.</i>

101
00:07:17.640 --> 00:07:19.437
<i>Hither greenan bairn
claideb-</i>

102
00:07:19.560 --> 00:07:22.393
- Aah! Aah!
- You all right? Nice try. Willow.

103
00:07:30.160 --> 00:07:33.914
Farmers!
Cherlindrea sends me farmers!

104
00:07:34.040 --> 00:07:37.316
Whew! The Nelwyn
really butchered that one.

105
00:07:37.440 --> 00:07:39.192
I'm sorry. Raziel.

106
00:07:39.400 --> 00:07:43.439
- You want out?
- Easy. We can pick a lock. Come on.

107
00:07:43.560 --> 00:07:45.357
No. No. no.
Like this!

108
00:07:45.480 --> 00:07:47.277
I know what I'm doing.
It's my spear. Leave it alone.

109
00:07:47.400 --> 00:07:51.109
Let me do it.
Out of the way. rodents.

110
00:07:52.200 --> 00:07:53.872
Take your hand off that.

111
00:07:54.000 --> 00:07:58.198
<i>You leave that alone.
you stupid. fat Daikini!</i>

112
00:07:58.320 --> 00:07:59.833
Ow!

113
00:07:59.960 --> 00:08:01.951
Dust of broken hearts.

114
00:08:12.280 --> 00:08:14.953
Ha. ha! You are free!

115
00:08:15.080 --> 00:08:19.119
Come on. Madmartigan.
Let's get Elora Danan out of here.

116
00:08:19.240 --> 00:08:23.153
- Yeah. It'll be fun.
- Come on!

117
00:08:34.440 --> 00:08:38.228
- Are you all right?
- Yeah.

118
00:08:38.360 --> 00:08:40.316
I feel... good.

119
00:08:40.440 --> 00:08:43.796
- The dust of broken hearts.
- Ah-

120
00:08:43.920 --> 00:08:46.354
Hey. come on!

121
00:08:51.600 --> 00:08:54.558
<i>- Let me see!
- Let me see. You always see.</i>

122
00:08:54.680 --> 00:08:56.955
There's Elora. right there.
on those furs.

123
00:08:59.320 --> 00:09:01.356
Hey. wait! Leave this to us.

124
00:09:01.480 --> 00:09:04.040
- It's too dangerous for you.
- Only one of us should go in there.

125
00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:06.833
I've had experience in this sort
of thing. I know what I'm doing.

126
00:09:33.040 --> 00:09:35.793
Uh-oh.

127
00:09:35.920 --> 00:09:39.629
Wait. Shh. No! No!

128
00:09:49.800 --> 00:09:52.439
<i>- I love you.
- Madmartigan!</i>

129
00:09:52.560 --> 00:09:55.358
- What are you doing?
- Take the baby and go! Come on!

130
00:09:55.480 --> 00:09:57.311
<i>Come on!</i>

131
00:10:07.000 --> 00:10:09.070
- Oh. Sorsha.
- Oh!

132
00:10:10.800 --> 00:10:13.598
Wake from this hateful sleep.

133
00:10:13.720 --> 00:10:15.950
<i>It deprives me of your beauty.</i>

134
00:10:16.080 --> 00:10:19.834
- The beauty of your eyes-
- One move. jackass.

135
00:10:19.960 --> 00:10:22.235
and you really will be a woman.

136
00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:27.309
You are my sun! My moon!

137
00:10:27.440 --> 00:10:31.672
My starlit sky.
Without you. I dwell in darkness.

138
00:10:31.800 --> 00:10:35.679
- I love you.
- What are you doing here?

139
00:10:35.800 --> 00:10:38.951
Your power has enchanted me.
I stand helpless against it.

140
00:10:39.080 --> 00:10:40.877
Come to me. now.

141
00:10:41.000 --> 00:10:43.309
Tonight. let me worship you
in my arms.

142
00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:46.000
- Get away from me!
- I love you!

143
00:10:46.160 --> 00:10:48.435
Stop saying that!

144
00:10:48.560 --> 00:10:52.599
How can I stop the beating of my heart?
It pounds like never before.

145
00:10:52.720 --> 00:10:55.154
- Out of fear.
- Out of love!

146
00:10:55.280 --> 00:10:57.589
I can stop it.
I'll kill you.

147
00:10:57.720 --> 00:11:00.518
Death. next to love.
is a trivial thing.

148
00:11:03.240 --> 00:11:05.595
Your touch is worth
100.000 deaths.

149
00:11:10.280 --> 00:11:12.840
What goes on here?

150
00:11:16.720 --> 00:11:18.597
Deceiver!

151
00:11:20.120 --> 00:11:21.872
<i>Stop him!</i>

152
00:11:30.480 --> 00:11:32.948
<i>Captain. get up!</i>

153
00:11:43.000 --> 00:11:47.437
<i>You are great.</i>

154
00:11:47.560 --> 00:11:50.279
Get on that shield!

155
00:12:01.200 --> 00:12:03.634
Sorsha!

156
00:12:06.200 --> 00:12:08.111
After them!

157
00:12:14.640 --> 00:12:16.835
Whoa! Hey!

158
00:12:21.520 --> 00:12:23.317
<i>They're getting away!</i>

159
00:12:31.840 --> 00:12:33.956
<i>- Follow me. Rool. I don't know.
- Where are you?</i>

160
00:12:34.080 --> 00:12:38.073
- Aah! Ooh.
- Oh. no. where did everybody go?

161
00:12:38.200 --> 00:12:40.031
Maybe it was
something we said.

162
00:13:31.920 --> 00:13:34.832
Ohh-h-h-h!

163
00:13:55.200 --> 00:13:57.111
Madmartigan!

164
00:14:13.240 --> 00:14:17.279
- Madmartigan!
- What the hell happened up there?

165
00:14:17.400 --> 00:14:19.630
You started spouting poetry.

166
00:14:19.760 --> 00:14:22.194
- Poetry?
- Yeah.

167
00:14:22.320 --> 00:14:25.392
"I love you. Sorsha.
I worship you. Sorsha. "

168
00:14:25.520 --> 00:14:27.317
You almost got us killed!

169
00:14:27.440 --> 00:14:29.237
"I love you. Sorsha"?

170
00:14:29.360 --> 00:14:31.635
I don't love her.
She kicked me in the face.

171
00:14:31.760 --> 00:14:34.957
I hate her! Don't I?

172
00:14:37.160 --> 00:14:39.435
Kael! Kael!

173
00:14:39.560 --> 00:14:42.074
Nockmaar soldiers!

174
00:14:44.000 --> 00:14:47.276
<i>Hide! Get the children! Come on!</i>

175
00:14:50.000 --> 00:14:51.797
- Get the children!
- They're after us!

176
00:14:51.920 --> 00:14:54.832
Come on. Follow me. Quick!
Come on! Move!

177
00:15:10.680 --> 00:15:13.319
I knew you'd
get out of that rattrap.

178
00:15:15.840 --> 00:15:17.637
You left me to die. Airk.

179
00:15:17.760 --> 00:15:20.877
I probably saved your life.
We were slaughtered and I lost a lot-

180
00:15:21.000 --> 00:15:23.195
<i>Shh! Quiet!</i>

181
00:15:24.280 --> 00:15:26.077
<i>Tear this village apart!</i>

182
00:15:26.200 --> 00:15:30.398
<i>Look everywhere!
Find the child!</i>

183
00:15:38.960 --> 00:15:42.236
Shh!

184
00:15:47.880 --> 00:15:49.677
Shh-shh-shh!

185
00:16:04.760 --> 00:16:07.638
Tell Sorsha
I search the north bank!

186
00:16:07.760 --> 00:16:09.557
- Hah! Hah!
- Yes. General.

187
00:16:22.160 --> 00:16:24.116
Quiet. Shh!

188
00:16:42.760 --> 00:16:45.558
- Sorsha!
- Back.

189
00:16:45.680 --> 00:16:47.272
Back!

190
00:16:53.720 --> 00:16:56.109
Back!

191
00:16:56.240 --> 00:17:00.279
- Keep the baby quiet.
- She needs to be changed.

192
00:17:00.400 --> 00:17:02.072
- Nockmaar scum!
- You'll never defeat us.

193
00:17:02.200 --> 00:17:03.918
- Give up the baby!
- Shut up!

194
00:17:05.840 --> 00:17:07.432
What does Bavmorda want
with this baby. anyway?

195
00:17:07.560 --> 00:17:09.198
She's a princess.

196
00:17:09.320 --> 00:17:10.992
<i>- We're taking her to Tir Asleen.
- Tir Asleen?</i>

197
00:17:11.120 --> 00:17:13.873
Even if you could find it. peck.

198
00:17:14.000 --> 00:17:16.230
she's right- you'd never
get past the Nockmaar army.

199
00:17:16.360 --> 00:17:18.669
There's an even bigger army
at Tir Asleen.

200
00:17:18.800 --> 00:17:21.155
<i>If we can just get there-</i>

201
00:17:24.440 --> 00:17:27.034
I've lost more than half my men
fighting Bavmorda.

202
00:17:27.160 --> 00:17:29.594
Now you and this peck
are gonna take her on?

203
00:17:29.720 --> 00:17:32.792
You always told me you served
no one. Madmartigan.

204
00:17:32.920 --> 00:17:34.751
Since when are you a crusader?

205
00:17:37.000 --> 00:17:40.072
He's not gonna help you. peck.

206
00:17:40.200 --> 00:17:42.077
He's a worthless thief.

207
00:17:43.440 --> 00:17:45.715
I'm not a thief. Airk.

208
00:17:45.840 --> 00:17:48.638
He's not a thief.

209
00:17:48.760 --> 00:17:50.876
Are you?

210
00:18:04.880 --> 00:18:08.509
I serve the Nelwyn. Airk.

211
00:18:13.040 --> 00:18:15.508
- Want to come with us?
- You'll never make it. Madmartigan.

212
00:18:17.400 --> 00:18:19.231
Then once again
we say goodbye.

213
00:18:32.520 --> 00:18:35.751
- Over here!
- Sorsha!

214
00:18:35.880 --> 00:18:39.077
Weapons down or she's dead!

215
00:18:44.080 --> 00:18:45.718
Hyah! Hyah!

216
00:18:51.120 --> 00:18:53.918
- Hyah!
- Get to your horses! After 'em!

217
00:19:38.240 --> 00:19:40.595
This way!
This way!

218
00:19:40.720 --> 00:19:43.280
As the crow flies. you fools!

219
00:19:49.920 --> 00:19:52.593
- You're holding me too tight!
- I don't want you to get away.

220
00:19:52.720 --> 00:19:57.316
<i>Why? Because I'm your sun.
your moon. your starlit sky?</i>

221
00:19:58.880 --> 00:20:00.996
Get your hair out of my face.
or I'll chop it off.

222
00:20:04.720 --> 00:20:08.429
Did I really- Did I really
say those things last night?

223
00:20:08.560 --> 00:20:11.518
- In your tent?
- You said you loved me.

224
00:20:11.640 --> 00:20:13.995
- I don't remember that.
- You lied to me!

225
00:20:14.120 --> 00:20:16.350
No. I-

226
00:20:16.480 --> 00:20:18.755
I just wasn't myself last night.

227
00:20:18.880 --> 00:20:22.998
I suppose my power enchanted you.
and you were helpless against it.

228
00:20:23.120 --> 00:20:25.918
- Um. sort of.
- Then what?

229
00:20:26.040 --> 00:20:27.996
It went away.

230
00:20:28.120 --> 00:20:31.590
It went away?
"I dwell in darkness without you."

231
00:20:31.720 --> 00:20:33.676
- and it went away?
- Yeah.

232
00:20:44.400 --> 00:20:48.279
Whoa.

233
00:20:54.840 --> 00:20:57.115
Hurry! Kael's coming!

234
00:21:01.520 --> 00:21:03.670
Madmartigan. come on!
Now!

235
00:21:11.440 --> 00:21:14.830
Madmartigan. come on!

236
00:21:14.960 --> 00:21:17.554
They're coming! Away!

237
00:21:17.680 --> 00:21:19.830
Go on! Hyah!

238
00:21:36.200 --> 00:21:39.158
Whoa! Whoa!

239
00:21:39.280 --> 00:21:41.316
This way!

240
00:21:46.640 --> 00:21:50.269
Tir Asleen! At last. Tir Asleen!

241
00:22:00.760 --> 00:22:02.557
Hello?

242
00:22:02.680 --> 00:22:05.069
<i>Hello?</i>

243
00:22:09.080 --> 00:22:12.390
